      children: "Hey there, tarot enthusiasts! 🌟 Have you ever pondered on what constitutes a \"cult classic\"? It's like that hidden gem of a movie or TV show that never quite got the recognition it truly deserved back in the day. A treasure that has garnered a small but fiercely devoted fanbase. It's that kind of special love and understanding where only a chosen few truly grasp its essence. As they say, beauty lies in the eyes of the beholder, right? And if there's one game that perfectly embodies the essence of a video game cult classic, it's none other than EarthBound for the Super Nintendo. So, what's the scoop on EarthBound?"
